\DOC current_theory

\TYPE {current_theory : (void -> string)}

\SYNOPSIS
Returns the name of the current theory.

\DESCRIBE
Within a HOL session there is always a current theory. It is the
theory represented by the current theory segment together with its
ancestry. A call of {current_theory()} returns the name of the current
theory. Initially HOL has current theory {scratch}.

\FAILURE
Never fails.

\SEEALSO
export_theory, new_theory, print_theory.

\ENDDOC
